  ('optometrist-moex-00960', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-111-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '遠視+2.00D之國小學生，配戴正確的矯正眼鏡後，當他在家中寫功課時主要需用到下列何種功能？', '["立體視覺（stereopsis）", "暗適應能力（darkadaptation）", "瞳孔光反射作用（pupillarylightreflex）", "調節作用（accommodation）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "02b2f4655967", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ad9719516e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "111", "s": "1002", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 44, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00961', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-111-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一位成年人透過老花眼鏡上之ADD後可看清楚眼前33.33至100cm範圍內之物體，測量其總景深為1.00D， 此成年人老花眼鏡之ADD為何？', '["1.00D", "1.50D", "2.00D", "2.50D"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "02b2f4655967", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ad9719516e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "111", "s": "1002", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00962', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-111-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '夜間近視（nightmyopia）是因為環境昏暗影響瞳孔放大，使入射光聚在視網膜上的光斑擴散變大，此現象 屬於那一種像差？', '["球面像差（sphericalaberration）", "彗星像差（comaaberration）", "畸變（distortion）", "橫向色像差（lateralchromaticaberration）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "02b2f4655967", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ad9719516e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "111", "s": "1002", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 46, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-00963', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-111-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一位患者向你抱怨最近配戴眼鏡時，常會發生模糊的現象。調出病歷資料發現患者配戴的鏡片材質為聚碳 酸酯，雙眼度數為-10.00DS，且經過觀察後發現，模糊的現象發生在患者鏡架下滑時，也就是透過非光學 中心觀看才會出現。會有這樣的情況產生，判斷與何種像差有關？', '["橫向色像差", "縱向色像差", "場曲", "畸變"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:44+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "02b2f4655967", "answer_pdf_sha1": "3ad9719516e3", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111110", "c": "111", "s": "1002", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、111年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體...", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
